OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWindy this
OL,6,Fevening, but dry with sunny spells.
OL,7,FRemaining windy overnight with
OL,8,Fthickening cloud and isolated showers
OL,9,Farriving towards dawn, although some
OL,10,Fclear spells remain possible, mainly
OL,11,Fin the east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FOften cloudy to start with
OL,14,Fscattered showers, but sunny spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping and showers becoming more
OL,16,Fisolated, dying out later. Still windy
OL,17,Fhowever, and feeling cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
